133
00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:52.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır, teşekkürler.

134
00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:56.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tanrım. Peki bu sırada ne yapacaksın?

135
00:14:56.760 --> 00:15:00.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sıradan olmayan biriyle vakit geçireceğim.

136
00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:02.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
