<c.bg_transparent><i>Başkentte bacalardan çıkan duman</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>sokak seviyesinde kalıyor</i></c.bg_transparent>

156
00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:32.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
