587
00:52:46.880 --> 00:52:48.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır, bence beni çağırmasının nedeni

588
00:52:48.800 --> 00:52:51.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
sis meselesini halletme
şeklimi eleştirmekti.

589
00:52:51.960 --> 00:52:54.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama sis kalktı

590
00:52:54.240 --> 00:52:57.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
