617
00:54:45.800 --> 00:54:47.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hükümdar için bu uygun.

618
00:54:50.000 --> 00:54:51.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
